{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~kobsa/courses/ICS104/course-notes/general-design-rules.htm", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//w3c//dtd html 4.0 transitional//en\">\n<html><head>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n   <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=iso-8859-1\">\n   <meta name=\"GENERATOR\" content=\"Mozilla/4.71 (Macintosh; I; PPC) [Netscape]\"><title>Interaction-style independent design principles</title></head><body bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\n<font style=\"font-weight: bold;\" face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\">Interaction-style \nindependent</font></font><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> </span><font style=\"font-weight: bold;\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"> \ndesign principles</font><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> </span><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><br> &nbsp; \n</font> <ul> <li> <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\">Strive for \n<b>consistency</b> (constancy is a special type </font><a href=\"no-constancy.png\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"The linked image shows a sequence of screens that have non-constant elements\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down.gif\"></font></a><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\">)</font></li><ul> <li> <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\">a)\n      internal; \n</font></li>\n  \n    <li><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\">b) external with \nm<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">etaphor</span>, and other software</font></li>\n    <li><img style=\"width: 42px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"Finger pointing right\" src=\"../../../graphics/pointing-finger-right3.jpg\"><font style=\"font-style: italic;\" size=\"+1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">leads\n            to higher conformity with user expectations</span></font><br>\n    </li>\n\n  </ul>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n  <li><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\">Provide <b><a href=\"gdl-advance-info.htm\">advance information</a></b></font></li>\n  </ul>\n<ul>\n  <li><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\">Provide \n        immediate <b><a href=\"feedback.htm\">feedback</a></b></font> <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"></font></li>\n</ul>\n<ul> <li><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\">Permit easy \n  reversal of actions (<b><a href=\"UNDO.htm\">undo</a></b>) </font></li>\n</ul><ul> \n<li> <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><a href=\"error-avoidance.htm\"><b>Prevent errors</b></a>; \noffer <a href=\"error-handling.htm\">help in case of errors</a></font></li>\n</ul><ul> \n<li> <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\">Reduce short-term memory \nload </font><a href=\"rely-on-memory.jpg\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><font style=\"font-family: Monotype Sorts;\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><font size=\"6\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"The linked image shows a pop-up window that forces users to rely on their memories.\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"></font></font></font></a>&nbsp; <a href=\"rely-on-memory2.jpg\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><font style=\"font-family: Monotype Sorts;\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><font size=\"6\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><font style=\"font-family: Monotype Sorts;\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"The linked image shows a pop-up window that forces users to rely on their memories (search term not listed anymore)\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"></font></font></font></font></font></a> <a href=\"not-rely-on-memory2.jpg\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><font face=\"Wingdings\" size=\"6\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 22px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"The linked image shows a pop-up window that does NOT force users to rely on their memories (the search terms are repeated)\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_up.gif\"></font></font></font></a></li></ul><ul> <li> <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\">Cater \nto user <b>diversity</b>; allow for <a href=\"gdl-adapt-menu.htm\">personalization</a></font><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"> </font></li>\n</ul>\n<ul> \n  <li> <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\">(Let\n      \nthe user be in control)&nbsp; <a href=\"personified-computer.jpg\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"The linked image shows a screen interaction that suggests that the computer has an ego\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down.gif\"></a> </font></li>\n\n</ul></body></html>", "encoding": "ascii"}